    "Most of the essays from the students repeated output from ChatGPT more or less as is.",
    "These essays tended to include a number of factual errors, but more seriously, the essays lack depth and perspective.",
    "In Platt (2019), p. 444, Platt argued that Napoleon understood that it would be foolish for Britain to use its short-term advantage in technology to humiliate the Chinese.",
